description:
On Wednesday April 29, Jazz House Kids will present a masterclass with our Artistic Director and master bassist, Christian McBride.  This session will be a Rhythm Section Masterclass from the perspective of the bass player.  All instrumentalists are welcome!  

Just like all of our other sessions at the moment, this masterclass too will be conducted using ZOOM from 6:00p 7:15pm EST.  Invite your friends!  

RSVP:   Daniela Gonzalez (dgonzalez@jazzhousekids.org) and we will send you a pass code by email to get into the Zoom meeting
 
*We ask that each participant donate $10 to offset the costs of this new content on Venmo (@jazzhousekids) or on our website.  Please indicate in the note section which masterclass you will be attending.
fulltitle: Join Our Masterclass with Christian McBride
title: Join Our Masterclass with Christian McBride
